metadata.name: Backcountry I - Foreboding
metadata.description:
The feeling of foreboding enters the soul as the winter storm approaches and then engulfs the mountains, snow blasting you as darkness descends and light is extinguished. Fear of the unknown creeps into you as the wind howls and what was once familiar becomes alien and you become disorientated.

This image is No.1 in a small collection of 5 images.
